This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with video recognition and uses compressed video modalities. It could also belong to Multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with video data. The paper also proposes a method for distillation, which is a common technique in Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper mentions improving efficiency, which could be related to Neural Networks (cs.NE).
